WEBVTT

00:01.133 --> 00:05.533
Eldon Chance is a 53-year-old
forensic neuropsychiatrist.

00:05.653 --> 00:07.533
Of late, he is increasingly aware

00:07.534 --> 00:10.657
of a mental state he finds
to be muddied and unstable.

00:10.658 --> 00:12.218
Mrs. Blackstone?

00:12.219 --> 00:14.580
It says here that you separated
from your husband

00:14.581 --> 00:16.382
after he struck you in the face.

00:16.383 --> 00:19.265
Shortly thereafter, you became
aware of a second personality...

00:19.266 --> 00:20.506
Jackie Black.

00:20.507 --> 00:22.629
Jackie is daring and extroverted,

00:22.630 --> 00:24.310
He'll kill me. He said he would.

00:24.311 --> 00:26.192
I could be putting us both in danger.

00:26.193 --> 00:27.558
We're a predatory species.

00:27.559 --> 00:30.356
And next time we coincide
like this, that's on you.

00:30.357 --> 00:31.598
I will not accept

00:31.599 --> 00:33.932
this problem cannot be solved.

00:33.933 --> 00:37.443
This is D. D, meet Dr. Chance.

00:37.444 --> 00:39.045
You want to get down with this cop,

00:39.046 --> 00:40.607
you need to turn the tables on him.

00:40.608 --> 00:41.648
And how would I do that?

00:41.649 --> 00:42.584
You might hire it done.

00:43.570 --> 00:45.331
What you just did
was some kind of audition?

00:45.332 --> 00:46.653
There are no victims.

00:46.654 --> 00:48.294
Right now Blackstone is the feeder,

00:48.295 --> 00:49.455
you're the receiver.

00:49.456 --> 00:50.897
You've got to turn that around.

00:50.898 --> 00:52.578
They've been dating for five months?

00:52.579 --> 00:54.420
I just never thought
I would find out like this.

00:54.421 --> 00:56.502
We don't even know
for sure what this is.

00:56.503 --> 00:58.264
It's this boy's parents telling us

00:58.265 --> 00:59.545
that our daughter is a stalker.

00:59.546 --> 01:00.947
I'm not having trouble.

01:00.948 --> 01:02.228
When he's in love, he's totally in love.

01:02.229 --> 01:03.630
And then, when it's over

01:03.631 --> 01:04.899
and you want to try to still
be friends with him,

01:04.900 --> 01:06.753
that means you're obsessed
and you can't let go.

01:06.754 --> 01:08.554
<i>Hey, Doc. Detective Hynes.</i>

01:08.555 --> 01:11.037
Detective Blackstone stalked and
harassed you and your friend,

01:11.038 --> 01:12.431
and he beat you up.

01:13.360 --> 01:14.881
Stay away from my wife!

01:14.882 --> 01:16.442
Do you really still not see

01:16.443 --> 01:17.724
what dangerous ground this is?

01:17.725 --> 01:19.205
Or is that what you like about it?

01:19.206 --> 01:20.767
He's not omnipotent, Jaclyn.

01:20.768 --> 01:21.808
There are limits.

01:21.809 --> 01:23.169
Not until he's dead.

01:23.170 --> 01:24.290
You're my knight.

01:24.291 --> 01:25.571
Third move in the template.

01:25.572 --> 01:27.293
A single, fatal blow
to the aortic arch...

01:30.217 --> 01:31.909
Dad?

01:32.539 --> 01:33.940
Dad?

01:33.941 --> 01:36.743
We're gonna fix what's wrong with us.

01:36.744 --> 01:38.415
The both of us.

01:39.106 --> 01:40.787
That's what matters.

01:40.788 --> 01:42.829
So now he's gone... Blackstone.

01:42.830 --> 01:45.471
You were there, on the scene.

01:45.472 --> 01:46.993
What are the odds?

01:46.994 --> 01:51.638
A man who wanted me dead
now is dead because of me.

01:51.639 --> 01:52.919
I can't take that lightly.

01:52.920 --> 01:54.761
So, what happens now?

01:54.762 --> 01:56.266
Welcome to the neighborhood.

